---
title: Roasted Tomato and Mushroom Barley Salad with Fresh Bocconcini and Olives
description: We wanted to take the best elements of a great winter stew and turn them into a 'lighter' tasting version. Warm roasted tomatoes and red onion are the perfect sweet compliment to the 'meaty' mushroom. Nutty barley rounds out the flavour with creamy bocconcini to top!
